- Should I translate entire headers or preserve technical tokens/acronyms (for example VEP, AC, AF) as-is?

- Do you want compact German terms (one word or a single token) or natural German phrases (which may contain spaces) even if it results in more than one word per header?
Once you confirm, I’ll provide the full translated list in the specified format.
